        <updateDate>2009-09-10T21:33:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Plain Language in Health Insurance Act of 2009 - Requires any health insurance issuer, health plan, and federal health care program to use plain language in any publicly distributed document.</p> <p>Requires the Secretary of Health and Human Services to issue guidance on implementing such requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
